<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ 迦南760</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ, bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ,
 bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ, bié ràng shì jiè bǎ tā duó zǒu.
 bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ, fā zì nèi xīn shēn chù.
 bì méng yé hé huá de kàn gù. bì méng shén de cì fú.
 ruò bù shì yé hé huá jiàn zào fáng wū,
 jiàn zào de rén jiù wǎng rán láo kǔ.
 nǐ suǒ zuò de yī qiè, yào xiǎng méng shén de zhù fú,
 bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ, bǎ shàng hǎo de gěi zhǔ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>760</hymn_number>
</song>